you visiting family for the holiday or
just getting away

00:03:12.340 --> 00:03:18.440
ok so those are examples of direct
questions about things like the weather

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:25.110
and travel these are pretty safe topics
for starting a conversation which is why

00:03:25.110 --> 00:03:31.160
you might hear people use them so often
and you will also hear yes no questions

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:41.709
like can you believe and WH questions
like where are you going today killed

00:03:41.709 --> 00:03:49.510
those are direct questions now how about
those tag questions I talked about first

00:03:49.510 --> 00:03:52.810
what is that a question

00:03:52.810 --> 00:03:59.989
well to make a tag question you make a
comment then had a little question at

00:03:59.989 --> 00:04:07.660
the end for example you might say the
airport is quite busy isn't it or you

00:04:07.660 --> 00:04:14.280
could say you work in sales don't you
