funded program do you think you were in
the afternoon workshop where you

00:04:40.180 --> 00:04:41.420
now there are

00:04:41.420 --> 00:04:45.550
are couple of tricks to tag questions
first

00:04:45.550 --> 00:04:48.640
the question tag needs to match the
comment

00:04:48.640 --> 00:04:57.480
so with a beautiful day you need isn't
it because the day is the it that with

00:04:57.480 --> 00:05:04.540
you were in the morning workshop you
don't say isn't it instead we say we

00:05:04.540 --> 00:05:12.890
weren't you the subject has to match and
the verb tits has to match and here's

00:05:12.890 --> 00:05:18.540
the second thing about tag questions a
positive statement is followed by a

00:05:18.540 --> 00:05:24.380
negative tag question like a nice day
isn't it

00:05:24.380 --> 00:05:31.350
while a negative statement is followed
by a positive tag question like there

00:05:31.350 --> 00:05:35.670
isn't much snow is there does that make
sense

